 Patch Management Automation
Objectives
By the end of this lab, students will be able to:

Implement automated patch management workflows using Python
Create vulnerability scanning and assessment tools
Configure automated security updates for Linux systems
Generate patch deployment reports and monitoring dashboards
Implement rollback mechanisms for failed patches
Prerequisites
Before starting this lab, students should have:

Basic Linux command line proficiency
Python programming fundamentals
Understanding of package management (apt/yum)
Basic system administration knowledge
