Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Permission denied errors

Solution: Ensure scripts have execute permissions (chmod +x)
Use sudo for system-level operations
Check user is in sudo group
Issue: Package installation fails

Solution: Run sudo apt update first
Check disk space with df -h
Review /var/log/apt/ logs for details
Issue: Lynis not found

Solution: Install with sudo apt install lynis
Verify installation with which lynis
Check PATH environment variable
Issue: Reports not generating

Solution: Ensure reports/ directory exists
Check write permissions on directory
Verify JSON serialization of data structures
